snippet.title: I Hate This Place Reveal Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2025
snippet.description:
Bloober Team and Skybound Entertainment joined forces to reveal I Hate This Place, an open-world survival game based on the Kyle Starks comic of the same name. It's coming to PC in 2025.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #ihatethisplace

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
